## clinvar_tool v0.1.0

### Highlights
- ClinVar-driven variant extraction and reporting (VCF/VCF.gz)
- HGVS mapping (hgvs4variation + variation_allele)
- `sclc` mode: TP53/RB1, somatic pathogenic(/likely pathogenic), lung/SCLC phenotype filtering
- Optional annotations: gnomAD AF, COSMIC IDs/site/histology/count, TP53 functional notes, therapy evidence

### Linux binary
Build on Fedora/Linux:
```bash
cmake -S . -B build -G Ninja -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release
cmake --build build -j
./build/clinvar_tool --help
